# DAX Formulas for the Retail Sales Dashboard

This file contains the DAX measures used in building the Power BI Sales Dashboard.

---

## Customer Insights
- **Top Performing Customer**  
```
VAR TopCust =
    CALCULATE (
        FIRSTNONBLANK ( FactsSales[Customer Name], 1 ),
        TOPN ( 1, VALUES ( FactsSales[Customer Name]), [Total Sales], DESC )
    
    )
RETURN
TopCust 

## Product Insights
- **Top Selling Product**
``` 
VAR TopProd =
    CALCULATE (
        FIRSTNONBLANK ( FactsSales[Product Name], 1 ),
        TOPN ( 1, VALUES ( FactsSales[Product Name] ), [Total Sales], DESC )
    )
RETURN
TopProd


## Sales Insights
- **Total Sales**
Total Sales = SUM(FactsSales[Sales])
 
